lastfm.summary: "Got 'til It's Gone" is a song recorded by American singer Janet Jackson for her sixth studio album The Velvet Rope, featuring American rapper Q-Tip and Canadian singer Joni Mitchell. It was written by Jackson, Jam and Lewis, with additional writing by René Elizondo Jr. and Kamaal Ibn Fareed. The song was produced by Jackson, Jam and Lewis. The track was released as the record's lead single on September 22, 1997. A Mark Romanek-directed music video for the song won Janet a Grammy Award for Best Music Video – Short Form. Read more on Last.fm.
lastfm.title: Got 'Til It's Gone
